title: Funeral.Boss.S01E01.The.Harris.Way.VeroVenlo
description:
Bill Harris, Funeral Director, owns his own funeral home and employs his four, vivacious children - William III, Windall, 
Westley, and Tiara - who hope to eventually take over the business. 
Watch as this family delivers incredibly touching and personalized celebrations of life, 
while sometimes getting themselves into a bit of trouble along the way
